                    </div>
                    <span>This is a very good beginner's book. The only problem is that Adobe Reader will not let you copy and paste the code samples. The function is disabled, and you have to type in all of the code by hand.<P>I am not sure I would buy this book again because of this. I have left this book behind and moved onto more user friendly books.<P>What a waste.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Great for newcomers</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
