                    <span>In our company, we have some junior programmers that I get to supervise. For them, this is essentially their first programming job. I was searching for a good introductory java book to help get them up to speed. After some travails, I narrowed it down to this book.<P>It explains enough about java to get new programmers off to a good start. Several of my guys said this book was highly "cool"! Glad they liked it.</span>
                  
              
